# OmniRoute Step-1: Vibeslop → Robust

**Branch:** `koosha/step-1-bun-ts7-bifrost`
**Date:** 2026-06-25
**Status:** IN PROGRESS (scaffold done; verify pending)

## Goal
Replace Next.js 16.2 + React 19.2 + TS 6 stack with **bun + hono + tsgo (TS 7 native) + bifrost** as the LLM routing base. Add **uv + Python 3.14** for any py-side work (discovery microservices).

## Stack swap

| From | To |
|---|---|
| Next.js 16.2 | hono on bun |
| React 19.2 routing | server-side hono routes |
| TypeScript 6 (tsc) | TS 7 native preview (`tsgo`) |
| Vitest | bun test |
| Ad-hoc provider code | `@maximhq/bifrost` |
| npm scripts | bun scripts |
| No Python | uv + pyproject.toml + .python-version (py 3.14) |

## Files added (this PR)

- `src/server.ts` — bun + hono entrypoint with /health, /v1/chat/completions, /v1/models, /discovery/*
- `src/bifrost/index.ts` — bifrost registry (16+ providers), /v1/models, /v1/chat/completions bridge
- `src/bifrost/sse.ts` — SSE streaming multiplexer for bifrost
- `src/discovery/providers.ts` — provider health checker (parallel HEAD probes)
- `src/discovery/index.ts` — /discovery/providers, /discovery/scan routes
- `pyproject.toml` — uv-managed py 3.14 deps (httpx, fastapi, pydantic)
- `.python-version` — `3.14`
- `tsconfig.json` — TS 7 native preview config

## Files preserved (not deleted)

- `app/` → moved to `legacy/app/`
- `pages/` → moved to `legacy/pages/`
- `next.config.js`, `next-env.d.ts` → moved to `legacy/`
- `components/`, `src/lib/`, `src/app/` → preserved as reference for step-2 parity

## Existing work folded in

- `issue-4595-bifrost-stream` WT (commit `37259d607 fix(api): finalize bifrost streaming usage on close`) → brought in as bifrost SSE module
- Sprint WTs (PR-006 OTel, PR-007 cost, PR-008 alerts, PR-009 health, PR-010 collector, PR-011 SRE CI, PR-012 budget, PR-013 chaos, PR-014 deps, PR-015 SBOM) → step-2 carries these forward

## Verification

- [ ] `bun install` succeeds
- [ ] `bun run typecheck` (tsgo) passes 0 errors
- [ ] `bun test` passes existing suite (or documents what was moved)
- [ ] `bun run build` → `dist/server.js`
